          <a href="https://hub.docker.com/r/kcapp/api" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external-link">
            <img src="/images/icons/docker.svg" alt="GitHub" class="brand-icon" style="margin-left: -1em;"/>
          </a>
        </p>

        <p><a href="https://github.com/kcapp/frontend/wiki/Latest_Changes" target="_blank">Latest Changes</a></p>
